    "These data served as the foundation for training our LSTM-BRNN networks using the software package PARROT (Methods) 38.",
    "The training was performed using a fivefold cross-validation for 500 epochs with a split of 64:16:20 for training:validation:test.",
    "We call the collection of trained networks that enable sequence-to-ensemble predictions ALBATROSS.",
    "We first began training the ALBATROSS R g network.",
    "After optimizing hyperparameters (Methods), we checked that ALBATROSS-derived radii of gyration matched the Mpipi-GG radii of gyration for the set of sequences presented in Fig. 1c."
